      <h1 style="font-size:2.25rem;margin-top:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Work Boots for Construction: 10 Picks Compared on Safety, Comfort & Real-World Durability</h1>
      <div style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.9rem">June 17, 2026 · 10 min read</div>
