      <p><strong>ASIN:</strong> B0F8B238YX</p>
      <p>This alternate <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F8B238YX?tag=sciencesolved-20" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank">Furuian Steel Toe Boots</a> variant shares the same core build — lightweight alloy steel toe, slip-resistant rubber outsole, and breathable mesh lining — but uses a different last that runs slightly narrower. Several verified buyers report this version fits snugger than the standard Furuian, making it a useful alternative if the main model feels loose around the heel or midfoot. Both clock 4.2 stars for a reason: at this price point, you get legitimate steel toe protection and all-day walkability without the premium markup.</p>
